<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">[root@localhost ~]# grep -q </span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379">"s"</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF"> a.txt    </span><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic">## -q选项表示静默输出</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
